import React from 'react'
import { Box,FormLabel,TextField } from '@mui/material'
const AddBook = () => {
  return (
    <form action=''>
      <Box display='flex'flexDirection="column" justifyContent={'center'} maxWidth='700' alignContent={'center'} alignSelf='center' mr={'auto'} marginTop='10'></Box>
      <FormLabel>Name</FormLabel>
<TextField margin='normal' fullWidth variant='outlined'name='Name'/>
<FormLabel>Author</FormLabel>
<TextField margin='Author' fullWidth variant='outlined'name='Author'/>
<FormLabel>Description</FormLabel>
<TextField margin='Description' fullWidth variant='outlined'name='Description'/>
<FormLabel >Price</FormLabel>
<TextField type={''} margin='normal' fullWidth variant='outlined'name='Price'/>
    </form>
  )
}

export default AddBook
